WEBVTT

00:01.170 --> 00:07.310
All right now that we're done with the pleasantries in this chapter we need to set up shop.

00:07.520 --> 00:14.060
Now in my opinion this is the most difficult chapter in the entire series because there are some things

00:14.060 --> 00:20.210
either you or your I.T. people are going to have to do to coordinate Google Apps with business with

00:20.210 --> 00:21.430
your host server.

00:21.770 --> 00:24.710
That's going to be different for every host server that's out there.

00:24.710 --> 00:28.490
But I think I've got a good idea on how I'm going to teach this.

00:28.610 --> 00:32.160
Once you get over this hurdle and believe me it's not really that big of a hurdle.

00:32.930 --> 00:38.540
Once you get over it I would say it's not necessarily down hill but you get into the fun of setting

00:38.540 --> 00:40.750
things up because now it's going to work for you.

00:40.760 --> 00:48.880
So this chapter is the most crucial chapter in getting Google Apps for business up and running.

00:49.010 --> 00:49.660
You're ready.
